  VERDICT (round 2):
  - No numerical RH violation detected (expected)
  - GUE distribution fits zero spacings better than Poisson
  - Truncation at K=50 inadequate for Li proof-grade test
  - Round 2 provides 4 computational signals orthogonal to R1 ladder
  - BT-541 resolution: 0/1 MISS (RH unresolved by this attack)
